title: Report: One Direction's Louis Tomlinson Expecting a Baby Girl
text:
Report: One Direction's Louis Tomlinson Expecting a Baby Girl Posted just a moment ago 
ABC/FredLee (LONDON) -- We've known since last summer that One Direction member Louis Tomlinson's girlfriend, stylist Briana Jungwirth, is pregnant with their child. Now In Touch magazine is reporting the couple's expecting a baby girl. 
“Louis’ family is thrilled. They would have been happy either way, but they know he will be a great dad to a daughter because he has six sisters. And Briana’s over the moon!” the magazine writes, quoting an unidentified source. 
People magazine first reported the pregnancy in July, which Jungwirth has since confirmed.
